<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For allotments under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s15042">section 15042 of this title</ref>, there are authorized to be appropriated $32,000,000 for fiscal year 2001 and such sums as may be necessary for each of fiscal years 2002 through 2007.</p>
